px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个硕士专业学位授权类别，涉及</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">39</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个二级学位点。有</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">3</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级重点学科、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级重点（培育）学科、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级研究生教育创新基地、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个国家级特色专业、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级品牌专业、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">16</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">门省级精品类课程、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">3</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级教学团队。有</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">1</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个国家级专业综合改革项目、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">5</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;">个省级专业综合改革项目、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;">9</span><s